ed="T" n="0721c03"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0721c03"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042321">大聖千福寺</placeName><persName key="A000888">飛錫</persName>傳<ptr target="#n197"/></head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0721c04"/><persName key="A000888">釋飛錫</persName>，未知何許人也。神氣高邈，識量過<lb
ed="T" n="0721c05"/>人。初學律儀，後於天台法門「一心三觀」<ptr type="glossary" target="#g393"/>，與<lb
ed="T" n="0721c06"/>沙門<persName key="A009174">楚金</persName>棲心研習。<date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141993438" notAfter-iso="+0745-09-30"><name>天寶</name>初</date>遊于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京闕</ref>，多<lb
ed="T" n="0721c07"/>止<placeName key="PL000000042657"><placeName>終南</placeName><placeName>紫閣峯</placeName><placeName>草堂寺</placeName></placeName>。屬<persName key="A000095">不空</persName>當途<ptr type="glossary" target="#g394"/>傳譯，慎<lb
ed="T" n="0721c08"/>選英髦，<persName key="A000888">錫</persName>預其數，頻登筆受<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>、潤文<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g70"/>之任。<date key="j20006032000603" when-iso="+0765-05-13"><persName key="A004379">代<lb
ed="T" n="0721c09"/>宗</persName><name>永泰</name>元年四月十五日</date>，奉詔於<placeName key="PL000000042358"><placeName>大明宮</placeName><placeName>內<lb
ed="T" n="0721c10"/>道場</placeName></placeName>同義學<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g395"/>沙門<persName key="A000540">良賁</persName>等十六人參譯《仁王<lb
ed="T" n="0721c11"/>護國般若經》<ptr target="#n150"/>并《密嚴經》<ptr target="#n199"/>。先在多羅葉時，並是<lb
ed="T" n="0721c12"/>偈頌，今所譯者多作散文。<persName key="A000095">不空</persName>與<persName key="A000888">錫</persName>等及<lb
ed="T" n="0721c13"/>翰林學士<persName key="A009172">柳抗</persName><ptr target="#n396"/>重更詳定，<persName key="A000888">錫</persName>充證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>正員，<lb
ed="T" n="0721c14"/>辭筆<ptr type="glossary" target="#g397"/>不愧斯職也。</p>
    <p><lb
ed="T" n="0721c15"/>系曰：<persName key="A000888">錫</persName>外研<name>儒</name>、<name>墨</name>，其筆仍長，時多請其論<lb
ed="T" n="0721c16"/>譔，如<persName key="A001707">忠<roleName>國師</roleName></persName>、<persName key="A009174">楚金</persName>等碑。與<placeName key="PL000000009739">晉陵</placeName><persName key="A009173">德宣</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013012">吳興</placeName><persName key="A008833">晝<lb
ed="T" n="0721c17"/><roleName>公</roleName></persName>同獵廣原，不知鹿死何人之手。然<persName key="A009173">宣</persName>、<persName key="A000888">錫</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0721c18"/>二公亦有不羈之失，緣飾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g398"/>過其實。如<persName key="A008833">晝<roleName>公</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0721c19"/>合<name>建中</name><ptr type="glossary" target="#g35"/>之體，儗事得其倫。唯虛與實，不可<lb
ed="T" n="0721c20"/>同日也。</p>
